abstract = {The proceedings contain 86 papers. The topics discussed include: targeted watermark removal of a SVD-based image watermarking scheme; practical intelligent modeling of three-phase induction machine; metamorphic malware categorization using co-evolutionary algorithm; a payment recommender model to increase mutual trust between sellers and buyers in e-marketplaces; proposing an evolutionary method based on maximization precision of group recommender systems; novel resource assignment method for balancing the inter-cell interference in OFDM cellular networks; bloom filter-based IP traceback on Netfilter opensource framework; decision functions estimation using inclined planes system optimization algorithm; a new method for evaluating cloud computing user behavior trust; intrusion detection system based on multi-layer perceptron neural networks and decision tree; and ARIMA-modeling based prediction mechanism in object tracking sensor networks.},
